moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而做仔嘅亦都一樣<span class=\"blue\">（好有米靚仔嘅咪就可以player點咁)</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算有一方面<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"teal\">未完全滿足</span></span>對方都仲好過再花其他額外嘅時間同資源投放係一個<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"violet\">要重新認識或者建立真感情嘅人身上</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為身上有可持續性嘅發展空間，<strong><span class=\"gold\">［size=6]即係有本錢[/size=6]</span>[/b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">冇咗你佢要填補嘅損失（即係喺出面搵返個同你差唔多嘅質素）係大於繼續用心維繫呢段關係，嗰樣嘢你冇嘅你咪喺其他方面搭夠去囉，</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個人嘅價值係取決於你係對方嘅生活中帶唔帶到好處，不斷提升自己嘅價值一方面可以令對方對自己上心忠誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一方面可以令自己襯得起對方唔會有自卑感，關係上卑微嘅情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為你知道你自身所擁有嘅價值係值得對方為你付出或犧牲，可能呢一度講嘅付出有啲令人誤會，係指受下脾氣、少啲時間同朋友玩、讓下步、磨合等，所以你同樣唔會擔心佢會搵第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁樣講好經濟學，係利益最大化咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但無可否認現實的確如此係咁，我哋會諗如果對方係真係夠愛自己嘅話，就算幾差都會接受自己，但係諗接受幾差嘅佢嘅一個過程裏面，其實都係不自覺[b]<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">含有衡量佢所有嘅價值好與差</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可唔可以抵觸或者，互補會唔會改到，對長遠有冇影響，自身又係咪真係咁重視嗰一方面嗰啲，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">到頭來咪又係講緊值唔值得嘅問題</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"small\">此文謹代表本人之立場，並非老強各人去接受or話個個都系咁</span>套已戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7770ba707d8738c0f52583197e3f5d6e246019","tid":2199306,"uid":9392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母五顏六色 睇撚到阿叔眼花"},{"pid":"044b8ff138fecd20aabcb1fa8cbf26566855b9fb","tid":2199306,"uid":221336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a7770ba707d8738c0f52583197e3f5d6e246019","tid":2199306,"uid":9392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母五顏六色 睇撚到阿叔眼花"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"真，睇撚到啊叔眼盲，啲藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}